OL,3,CEastEnders star says she had to use
OL,4,Cfoodbank after being treated for cancer
OL,6,FCleveleys-based former EastEnders
OL,7,Factress Cheryl Fergison says she had
OL,8,Fcash problems and was forced to use a
OL,9,Ffood bank after being treated for womb
OL,10,Fcancer.
OL,12,FFergison, who played Heather Trott on
OL,13,Fthe BBC soap from 2007 until 2012 -
OL,14,Fand appeared in Celebrity Big Brother
OL,15,Fand The IT Crowd - was diagnosed in
OL,16,F2015, and spoke out about her
OL,17,Fcondition in April 2024.
