OL,3,CEastEnders star says she had to use
OL,4,Cfoodbank after being treated for cancer
OL,6,FShe told OK! Magazine she had a
OL,7,Fhysterectomy and experienced early
OL,8,Fonset menopause due to the treatment
OL,9,Fbefore being given the all-clear.
OL,11,FShe told a national newspaper her
OL,12,Ftreatment forced her to stop acting,
OL,13,Fwhich caused her money issues, as well
OL,14,Fas mental health problems.
OL,16,FFergison, 60, revealed she had been
OL,17,Fsupported financially by former
OL,18,FEastEnders colleague Dame Barbara
OL,19,FWindsor. But this help had run out
OL,20,Fafter Dame Barbara died in 2020 aged
OL,21,F83.
