OL,3,CEastEnders star says she had to use
OL,4,Cfoodbank after being treated for cancer
OL,6,F"I didn't have any money to do a
OL,7,Fweekly shop, I was trying to pay too
OL,8,Fmany debts," she said.
OL,10,F"It was a really difficult time. Lots
OL,11,Fof people can relate to it. You're
OL,12,Ftrying to find a penny. You're
OL,13,Fliterally looking down your settee to
OL,14,Fsee if you can find a quid."
OL,16,FShe told how she "cried and cried"
OL,17,Fafter being advised to use a foodbank
OL,18,Fby Citizens' Advice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
