OL,3,CEastEnders star says she had to use
OL,4,Cfoodbank after being treated for cancer
OL,6,F"How could I have been earning that
OL,7,Fmuch money and now I am here?," she
OL,8,Fasked.
OL,10,FHowever, since being supported by the
OL,11,Ffood bank, who Fergison called
OL,12,F"angels", she said she has not needed
OL,13,Ftheir help again.
OL,15,FInstead, Fergison said she has been
OL,16,Fable to return to work in pantos and
OL,17,Fsinging in restaurants.
OL,19,F"I hope other people can relate to it.
OL,20,FI really want to stress that food
OL,21,Fbanks are a service," she said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
