OL,3,CEastEnders star says she had to use
OL,4,Cfoodbank after being treated for cancer
OL,6,F"They're there for you to use so
OL,7,Fplease do not feel embarrassed or that
OL,8,Fit's a weakness. Whatever the reason,
OL,9,Fyou deserve help. We have a right to
OL,10,Fbe able to live like a human being and
OL,11,Fdo it in a dignified way."
OL,13,FFergison has also been in Little
OL,14,FBritain sketches and Your Face Sounds
OL,15,FFamiliar, and appeared in the Netflix
OL,16,Fshow Hard Cell with Catherine Tate in
OL,17,F2022.
